div.div: Data on LFT are registred in iRODS
Start: session is over, share is locked and metadata files are present

ol.li: each file gets UUID KV pair
if a /SubmissionID collection is newly created, the submission_metadata.json is harvested and KV pairs are attached to the /SubmissionID collection
session_metadata.json is harvested and KV pairs are attached to the /SessionID collection

div.div: End: All files are registered in iRODS, labelled with UUID and submission and session collections have KV pairs from metadata files
